## Usage Guidelines

### Pair with Codex Panel

1. Open Codex panel in VS Code (many users prefer right side)
2. Use context from opened files and selected code
3. Write shorter prompts for faster, more relevant results

### Delegate to Cloud

For larger tasks:
1. Offload to Codex in the cloud
2. Track progress in VS Code
3. Review results and open locally for finishing touches
4. Context remains consistent across cloud and local work

### ChatGPT macOS App Integration (macOS only)

1. Launch ChatGPT macOS app
2. Select "Work with VS Code"
3. ChatGPT can now answer questions and make simple edits

